    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Fireteam Specialist:</strong> 10th level</em></p>\n<p>While your companion is within 5 feet of you, you can use your bonus action to begin a coordinated </p>\n<p>maneuver. For the next minute, while you and your companion are within 5 feet of each other and neither of you are wielding a shield, you each gain a bonus to AC equal to half your proficiency bonus.</p>\n<p>This effect ends early if either you or your companion are incapacitated or die. Once you've used this feature, you can't use it again until you complete a long rest.</p>",
